{"tid":2076604,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩食物又易整又平又健康","createTime":"2020-06-23T15:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T17:41:46.000Z","uid":240665,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"65d983cecca56be924e8670fcbe5aae18d2e2473","tid":2076604,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:42:36.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好係用水沖完就食得嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n倒如奇亞籽咁<br />\n與其食個五十蚊難食到嘔嘅茶記飯<br />\n我寧願求其食啲嘢落肚算"},{"pid":"69ceb095bcfd8ff1f33512501501ea9270579666","tid":2076604,"uid":86614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"杯面"},{"pid":"27160f4f42363d1de8d19f4f2507435cecba0c0a","tid":2076604,"uid":1095,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"chia seed 好似會致癌"},{"pid":"f22746b28b39248636ee152f2aa0183740e0b824","tid":2076604,"uid":165224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27160f4f42363d1de8d19f4f2507435cecba0c0a","tid":2076604,"uid":1095,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"chia seed 好似會致癌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"真？"},{"pid":"ef87d33d93e8d10ed681f972409425fa55cdda21","tid":2076604,"uid":165224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:47:53.000Z","msg":"整啲overnight oats? a&ccedil;ai bowl都好快"},{"pid":"7ba0015a392da38a3c0b39167b94c6edf1afe514","tid":2076604,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:50:53.000Z","msg":"蛋"},{"pid":"a657801ed912ff9c2751e5354aa3e1abca0814b5","tid":2076604,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"香蕉囉"},{"pid":"0b99e49c1df29c497af496649e5f182dbf57d421","tid":2076604,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef87d33d93e8d10ed681f972409425fa55cdda21","